{"title":"金沙江畔（二首）","authors":["张永权"],"dates":[{"year":1990,"month":8,"day":20}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"金沙江畔（二首）"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"张永权"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"石鼓"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"石鼓、石鼓，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一面石头做成的沉沉大鼓，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"月亮一般浑圆，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"太阳一样闪烁。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"鼓声穿过世纪的烟云，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"响在风声里，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"响在江涛中。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"岁月的尘埃蒙不住"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"民族间那残酷的杀戮。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"走出鼓上的《大功纪胜歌》，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"是征夫的血汗，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"是寡妇的泪珠。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"石鼓一响，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"风在诉说，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"浪在悲歌。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"历史在鼓声里打上绑腿，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"闪闪的红星照亮了雪山峡谷，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一位姓贺的胡子将军，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"细眯着眼把石鼓抚摸。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"惊雷一声，雪山回应，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"金江欢呼！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"于是，在万里长江第一湾，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"石鼓有了新的传奇，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"鼓声从历史走进现实，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"响彻万里征途。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"金沙江大桥"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"跨过那江涛的狰狞，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"跨过那深峡的险峻，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"跨过那冰雪凝固的高山，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"跨过那世纪的层层战云，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"他在马背上吟成的诗篇，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"催人踏上新的征程！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"水拍云崖，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"卷去一江血泪，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"抚平累累伤痕。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"彩虹飞过了血染的历史，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"狂怒的大江，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"像牧女一样温顺。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"是五十年前的那双脚印，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"把基础打牢在奔腾的江心，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"几代人用血汗浇铸，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"才完成了这巨大的工程。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"虽然它比不上武汉南京大桥宏伟，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"却也能抗九级巨浪十级台风！"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":8,"page_end":8}